# Module 1111 AI Factory

Use `station-slots/` as the visible station contract. Use `.claude/agents/` only when running in a
runtime that needs Claude-style sub-agent files.

Run one feature from `feature.md` through the stations in this order:

`100,200,300,400,500,700,800,900,600,1000`

Follow `handoff-map.yaml` for inputs and write each named output under `runs/<feature-slug>/`.
Append a transcript note after each station. Do not invent missing upstream context. Record a seam
or stop when the station cannot produce the named output from saved artefacts.

Use `PREFLIGHT.md`, `COST_GUARDRAILS.md`, and `MANUAL_RUN_PROMPTS.md` for setup, cost limits, and
manual guided prompts.
